features: Great Value Montessori Toys - Our wooden stacking burger toys contain 15 activity cards, a wooden base and 8 wooden ingredient pieces: lettuce, beef, onion, cheese, tomatoes, bread and egg. Lots of cards and treats, enough for kids to make burgers of all flavors, and the bright colors and realistic shapes will definitely catch the attention of kids and keep them hooked.

Funny Educational and Learning Toys - The order cards are double-sided, with illustrations of finished hamburgers and picture instructions on how to make hamburgers, you can play the role of customers, choose cards and let children make hamburgers according to the instructions on the menu, which will greatly improve kid's concentration, fine motor skills, hand-eye coordination, creativity and imagination.

Safe and Durable Stacking Toys - Our burger stacking toy is made of high-quality wood with a polished surface, which is not only smooth but also very durable, and all food ingredients pieces are made of odorless and non-toxic water-based paint, which guarantees the safety of kids in many aspects, and you can rest assured to hand it over children.

Stacking Toys with Storage Bag - Our burger stacking toys come in vivid shapes and colors to help kids learn about food in their lives, it’s definitely a great addition to the kitchen game. And the package is also equipped with a storage bag, which can help you store and take out toys easily, keep your room tidy and avoid losing toys at the same time. The super portable storage bag is also convenient to take the toy anywhere (school/party/travel).

Ideal Gift For Kids 3, 4, 5 Years Old - Fun, educational and safe, this Montessori toy is great for kids boys girls entertainment. And the toy also comes with a beautiful gift box, which is definitely the perfect gift for kids boys girls birthdays and holidays (Children's Day, Christmas, Halloween, Valentine's Day and New Year).

reviews.reviewText: My kids have hours of fun playing with this stackable burger! The cards are like tiny menus or instructions on how to put burger in a specific order. It also looks exactly how it is advertised that I love of course!
